These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different games are played: snooker, whist, mah-jongg, billiard
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, family, mystery
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, lacrosse, water-polo
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, cola, juice, milk
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 2. the person drinking water is not to the left of the person drinking water##8
 3. the person drinking milk is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
 5. the person drinking water is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
 6. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 7. the person playing whist is somewhere to the right of the person playing snooker##5
 8. the person watching mystery movies is between the person drinking cola and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
 9. the person drinking milk is the person watching family movies##1
10. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
11. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
12. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the right of the person playing whist##5
13. the person watching family movies is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8
14. the person playing whist is the person drinking juice##1
15. the person playing whist is not the person who's sport is ice-hockey##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Game         | snooker     | whist   | billiard | mah-jongg |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | mystery   | animation   | family  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey  | lacrosse  | water-polo  | cycling |
| Beverage     | water    | juice | cola     | milk    |

