.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, satire, musical, thriller
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, folk, reggae, soul
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, lacrosse, tennis
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, swisher, tiparillo, havana
 1. the person watching musical movies is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 2. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
 3. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the right of the havana-smoker##5
 4. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left##1
 5. the baccarat-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
 6. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 7. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
 8. the swisher-smoker is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 9. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
10. the person watching satire movies is not to the right of the fan of folk##8
11. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
12. the havana-smoker is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre      | documentary   | thriller     | musical    | satire |
| Music-Genre   | ambient  | soul      | reggae     | folk     |
| Sport         | climbing | lacrosse  | tennis     | cycling  |
| Cigar     | baccarat     | tiparillo | havana | swisher     |

