.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-17::.
House: ranch-style, palace, art-deco, craftsman
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, chess, magic-tricks, skydiving
4 different pets are kept: rat, frog, rabbit, turtle
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, british, german, italian
 1. the ranch-style house is on the left of the italian##1
 2. the ranch-style house is not to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
 3. the craftsman house is the owner of the frog##1
 4. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
 5. the palace house is somewhere to the right of the owner of the turtle##5
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the left of the owner of the rat##8
 7. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the palace house##3
 8. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the german##3
 9. the british is not to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
10. the owner of the rabbit is not the brazilian##6
11. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
12. the italian is on the left of the art-deco house##1
13. the owner of the turtle is not to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
14. the brazilian is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |      4       |
| House      | ranch-style      | craftsman  | art-deco | palace        |
| Hobby         | skydiving | chess   | baking   | magic-tricks |
| Pet   | turtle    | frog   | rabbit    | rat      |
| Nationality   | british   | italian | german   | brazilian    |

