.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, milk, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, sudoku, cooking, camping
There 4 different types of food: potato, kale, mango, pumpkin
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, scooter, subway, van
 1. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 2. the person eating pumpkin is not to the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
 3. the person eating potato is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person eating mango##5
 6. the person driving the van is the person drinking juice##1
 7. the person who's hobby is camping is not to the right of the person driving the van##8
 8. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
 9. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the right of the person drinking milk##8
10. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
11. the person eating potato is somewhere to the left of the person eating pumpkin##5
12. the person eating mango is somewhere to the left of the person eating kale##5
13. the person driving the subway is not to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1        |    2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | juice          | iced-tea | milk        | sprite    |
| Hobby         | camping | collecting   | sudoku | cooking  |
| Food         | mango           | potato     | pumpkin       | kale  |
| Transport   | van            | subway   | scooter     | quad-bike |

