.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-19::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, badminton, handball, soccer
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, card-games, puzzles, rock-climbing
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, fisherman, photographer, project-manager
House: cape-cod, palace, ranch-style, farmhouse
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not the person who's sport is handball##6
 2. the dancer is not to the left of the farmhouse house##8
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the palace house##1
 4. the dancer is not to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##8
 5. the fisherman is somewhere to the right of the photographer##5
 6. the ranch-style house is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##5
 8. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the left of the photographer##8
 9. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
10. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere between the farmhouse house and the project-manager##7
11. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |      2       |       3       |    4    |
| Sport    | handball        | badminton        | basketball        | soccer   |
| Hobby       | card-games      | camping      | rock-climbing | puzzles |
| Job         | project-manager | photographer | fisherman     | dancer  |
| House   | ranch-style          | cape-cod      | palace     | farmhouse  |

