.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different games are played: snooker, mah-jongg, go, canasta
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, game, chaman, ritmeester
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, romance, western
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, indie, jazz, reggae
 1. the person playing canasta is not to the left of the bluemaster-smoker##8
 2. the person playing go is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 3. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the right of the fan of jazz##5
 4. the ritmeester-smoker is the person watching western movies##1
 5. the person playing go is not the chaman-smoker##6
 6. the person watching adventure movies is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
 7. the person watching animation movies is not to the left of the chaman-smoker##8
 8. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
 9. the fan of jazz is in an even position##4
10. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
11. the person watching adventure movies is in an even position##4
12. the person playing go is between the chaman-smoker and the person playing canasta##2
13. the person playing canasta is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |       3       |     4      |
| Game         | canasta    | go   | snooker   | mah-jongg |
| Cigar           | bluemaster | game    | chaman | ritmeester    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance   | adventure | animation     | western    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop   | jazz      | indie         | reggae     |

 